Good morning Michael and my beautiful family! I love you guys so much! And I am thankful and blessed you guys chose to stay in my life when you didn't have to or required to after all the heart ache I have caused. I say these things now because it's not that I haven't forgiven myself, because I have. But through some more major step work and a book study on boundaries, I have come to realize I have become willing and absolutely Openminded to sit down with you and really really listen. If you ever feel the need that you still might need to. I don't believe I ever really did that. Before this last relapse I was still self absorbed in my own little world. Never really realizing that I thought I did this program for me and you guys the first time, but was actually doing it for you guys because it was do it or loss you guys forever. The way you guys are raising your children is the way I would have raised you guys if I didn't have so much guilt about getting high! I did not do right by you guys and I see that now. Sorry it's taken me so long! When I watch you guys with your children and see so much love and respect you all have for each other fills my soul with such joy! My sponsor says don't be so hard on myself. She said they could not have learned so much love if they were not given it from you too. As my other friend always says. She can't take the credit for the good, she gives that to God! Because she won't take the credit for bad. But what I see is good. Again anytime you ever want or need to talk I am always 100 percent here for all of you! My heart is full! You guys rock my world 🌎 all my love all my life!
